snippet.title: Actress Amber Rose House in Los Angeles || $4 Million || House Tour
snippet.description:
American model, stripper, fashion designer and actress, Amber Levonchuck, better known by her stage name Amber Rose has bought a new LA pad; she bought the mansion in the San Fernando Valley, Los Angeles for just under $4million.
The house boasts six bedrooms and eight bathrooms spread over two storeys. It’s got a library, a bar, several sitting areas and a kitchen with a slightly excessive total of three ovens and two dishwashers. It’s beautifully decorated, with high ceilings in most rooms, feature fireplaces, a statement staircase, neutral colour schemes and Mediterranean vibes throughout.
